# Visualize Paper Relation

This tool converts a Zotero JSON export into a visual citation graph.

## Quick Start

1. Install:

   pip install .

2. Run:

   vpr --zotero-json MyCollection.json --out-dir results

Outputs are saved in the specified folder.
